      ΔArf1
     </sup>
     -mCh were largely cytosolic (
     <xref ref-type="fig">
      Fig. 4, F-H and L-N
     </xref>
     ). These observations indicated that the Arf1 recruitment sites on both β1 and γ are required for targeting of AP-1 to the TGN/endosomes within cells.
